➜英语绘本故事《Elephant Work》
http://www.sohu.com/a/431574840_100171577	21299
<p><strong>《Elephant Work》</strong>绘本故事里，大象想找一份工作，可为什么它跑回了动物园呢？快来看看是怎么回事吧！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201113/356a0b76906d4aebbc82c3c898c14f8b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>The elephant stopped at our house, waving its big gray nose.</p>
<p>一只大象在我家门口停下了，挥舞着他那灰色的大鼻子。</p>
<p>“Do you have work for an animal with a very useful hose?” </p>
<p>“你这里有工作适合有软管的动物吗？”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201113/11f842e9013a4461b69a688d22152c1c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>“Come in! Come in!” my father cried.</p>
<p>“快进来，快进来”我爸爸大喊着，</p>
<p>“You answer all my wishes. You can do the laundry and a heap of dirty dishes.” </p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p>“你满足了我所有愿望。你可以洗衣服和一堆脏盘子。”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201113/41c5f0824f1f42178c2aa9cd0a8479b6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>“Wash the upstairs windows. Sweep and mop the floors. Clean the car and the garage, and don’t forget the doors.” </p>
<p>“清洗楼上的玻璃。打扫地板和拖地。清洗车和车库，不要忘了还有那些门。”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201113/90fcd195d6ad44a4b9b5cc743fa95414.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>“Stop!” bellowed the elephant. “That’s too much work to do!” </p>
<p>“停下”大象吼道。“有太多的工作要做了！”</p>
<p>Then with a snort, it turned away and ran back to the zoo. </p>
<p>随着一声喷鼻声，它转身跑回来动物园。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201113/62f5ab34fff34e4fa346e97c19e62da9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>